     <tr>\r\n            <td>Cuadrado v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0103n m\u1eebng sau khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 ba gi\u00fap Colombia h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ba Lan.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Colombia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:<br />\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<strong><br />\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-jose-pekerman-khen-colombia-da-dep-465-189469.html\">H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ba Lan, HLV Jose Pekerman khen Colombia \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-ba-lan-03-colombia-421-189468.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-loai-tu-rat-som-hlv-ba-lan-noi-gi-421-189467.html\">B\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm HLV Ba Lan n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-doi-tuyen-bi-loai-sau-hai-tran-dau-tien-world-cup-2018-465-189466.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-ba-lan-vs-colombia-461-189465.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia (B\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-gay-soc-sau-tran-ba-lan-03-colombia-421-189461.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c sau tr\u1eadn Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br />\r\nN.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"539","checkdouble":"189470"},{"date":"05:43 25/06","title":"\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Ba Lan th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/dau-la-nguyen-nhan-khien-dt-ba-lan-tham-bai-truoc-colombia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1ea1i Kazan Arena t\u1ed1i 24/6, \u0110T Ba Lan \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia trong th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u1eady \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u201cnh\u1eefng ch\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng\u201d?</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Senegal c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n nhau \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm, c\u1ea3 Ba Lan l\u1eabn Colombia \u0111\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i Kazan, \u201cnh\u1eefng ch\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng\u201d Ba Lan \u0111\u00e3 \u2018g\u00e3y c\u00e1nh\u2019 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia sau c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina (40'), Falcao (70') v\u00e0 Cuadrado (75'). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ba Lan. V\u1eady \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>1. H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu s\u1eafc b\u00e9n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Robert Lewandowski l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a NHM Ba Lan \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Bayern Munich c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi ghi t\u1edbi 16 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch s\u00e1nh ngang v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u2018Vua d\u1ed9i bom\u2019 Cristiano Ronaldo hay Romelu Lukaku.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Ba Lan th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Ba Lan th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Dau-la-nguyen-nhan-khien-DT-Ba-Lan-tham-bai-truoc-Colombia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Vi\u1ec7c Robert Lewandowski 't\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i' khi\u1ebfn\u00a0</em><i>\u0110T Ba Lan th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Lewy \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Ba Lan ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eaft. \u201cNh\u1eefng ch\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng\u201d d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n t\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga. Lewandowski \u2018t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i\u2019 trong 180 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 d\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 56 ph\u00fat cho m\u1ed7i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y th\u00ec ai c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Ba Lan \u0111\u1ec3 Colombia ghi li\u1ec1n 3 b\u00e0n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng danh d\u1ef1. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1eeb Robert Lewandowski nh\u01b0ng x\u00e9t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1ch quan, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i Ba Lan khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. Tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Colombia qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Colombia \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y kh\u00e1t khao gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 3-0 l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a James Rodriguez ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Colombia t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a NHM b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Comlombia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Bundesliga cho CLB Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi hai pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Rodriguez co 2 kien tao truoc Ba Lan\" title=\"James Rodriguez c\u00f3 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Thong-ke-Ba-Lan-vs-Colombia---Bang-H-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><strong>James Rodriguez c\u00f3 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 40 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1, pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a James Rodriguez \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap sao tr\u1ebb \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Barca, Yerry Mina c\u00f3 pha k\u1ebft th\u00fac g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 75, v\u1eabn l\u00e0 James v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n thi\u00ean t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 tung ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u1ecdn c\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 Juan Cuadrado b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 3-0 cho Colombia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 James Rodriguez thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Juan Quintero, g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho Radamel Falcao\u00a0nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 70 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Colombia \u0111\u00e3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1 \u2018m\u01b0\u1ee3t\u2019 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y trong khi Ba Lan l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u00f4ng \u00c2u s\u1edbm s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 d\u00f9 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n ki\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Ba Lan qu\u00e1 gi\u00e0 nua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">So v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y HLV Jose Pekerman \u0111\u00e3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u1edf \u0110T Colombia, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Yerry Mina v\u00e0 James Rodriguez -\u00a0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb, kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 \u0111ang khao kh\u00e1t c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">So v\u1edbi Colombia, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Ba Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 gi\u00e0 nua v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh thu\u1ed9c h\u00e0ng cao nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i khi \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ba Lan l\u00ean t\u1edbi 28.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ba Lan bi loai sau 2 tran thua lien tiep\" title=\"Ba Lan b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Nhung-diem-nhan-Ba-Lan-vs-Colombia---Bang-H-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c 'l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng' c\u1ee7a Ba Lan kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 Colombia</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Colombia, \u0110T Ba Lan \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 k\u1ec9 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng trong 40 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb Mina \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng l\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng con ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Ba Lan v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 danh ti\u1ebfng nh\u01b0 Lukasz Piszczek, tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 theo k\u1ecbp t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Colombia. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Ba Lan thua \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-ba-lan-vs-colombia-461-189465.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/clip-ban-thang-ba-lan-vs-colombia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-ba-lan-vs-colombia-461-189465.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia (B\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nNh\u1edd 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Yerri Mina, Radamel Falcao v\u00e0 Juan Cuadrado, Colombia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ba Lan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 \u0111\u1ec3 nhen nh\u00f3m hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ti\u1ec5n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nhat-ban-vs-senegal-461-189450.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/clip-ban-thang-nhat-ban-vs-senegal.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nhat-ban-vs-senegal-461-189450.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 2-2 Senegal (B\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nLi\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, Samurai xanh l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t san b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"538","checkdouble":"189472"},{"date":"06:10 25/06","title":"Thua Colombia, Robert Lewandowski ch\u00ea c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ba Lan thi\u1ebft ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/thua-colombia-robert-lewandowski-che-cau-thu-ba-lan-thiet-chat-luong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 l\u1ebd qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi s\u1edbm ph\u1ea3i chia tay World Cup 2018,  Robert Lewandowski ch\u00ea c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ba Lan thi\u1ebft ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn thua Colombia.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lewandowski im ti\u1ebfng<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Robert Lewandowski v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o cho \u0110T Ba Lan. Lewandowski tung ra \u0111\u1ebfn 7 trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 17 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ba Lan nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1eabn b\u1eb1ng 0.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi loai khoi World Cup 2018,  Robert Lewandowski che cau thu Ba Lan thiet chat luong.\" title=\"B\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018,  Robert Lewandowski ch\u00ea c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ba Lan thi\u1ebft ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/thua-colombia-robert-lewandowski-che-cau-thu-ba-lan-thiet-chat-luong.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018,  Robert Lewandowski ch\u00ea c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ba Lan thi\u1ebft ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nH\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0110T Ba Lan c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1 h\u01a1n khi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n sau hai tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u00f3n nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn thua khi\u1ebfn Ba Lan tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ph\u1ea3i chia tay World Cup 2018.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lewandowski ch\u00ea c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ba Lan&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 l\u1ebd qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i chia tay World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o, Robert Lewandowski ch\u00ea c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ba Lan thi\u1ebft ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng: &quot;C\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, hay t\u00ednh r\u1ed9ng ra \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i c\u00f4 \u0111\u01a1n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lewandowski v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khi Ba Lan ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 21h00 ng\u00e0y 28/6.<br />\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ba Lan t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dau-la-nguyen-nhan-khien-dt-ba-lan-tham-bai-truoc-colombia-421-189472.html\">\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Ba Lan th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/an-tuong-hinh-anh-cdv-phu-vang-san-kazan-trong-ngay-colombia-huy-diet-ba-lan-465-189470.html\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh C\u0110V ph\u1ee7 v\u00e0ng s\u00e2n Kazan trong ng\u00e0y Colombia h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ba Lan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-jose-pekerman-khen-colombia-da-dep-465-189469.html\">H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ba Lan, HLV Jose Pekerman khen Colombia \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-ba-lan-03-colombia-421-189468.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-loai-tu-rat-som-hlv-ba-lan-noi-gi-421-189467.html\">B\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm HLV Ba Lan n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-doi-tuyen-bi-loai-sau-hai-tran-dau-tien-world-cup-2018-465-189466.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"537","checkdouble":"189474"},{"date":"06:07 25/06","title":"Messi ch\u1ec9 chia tay \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/messi-chi-chia-tay-dt-argentina-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t \u0111i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf \u0110T Argentina ch\u1eebng n\u00e0o ch\u01b0a chinh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Lionel Messi t\u1eebng l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c. V\u00e0 n\u0103m nay, Argentina c\u1ee7a Messi \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y d\u1ea5y l\u00ean lo ng\u1ea1i El Pulga s\u1ebd gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb \u0110TQG sau m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi ch\u1ec9 chia tay \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lionel Messi ch\u1ec9 chia tay \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/petit-messi-khong-co-kha-nang-lanh-dao-nhu-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Messi mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n khi m\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Messi \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chia tay \u0110TQG ch\u1eebng n\u00e0o ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n tr\u00ean t\u1edd Mirror: &quot;World Cup l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Argentina v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 t\u00f4i n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i t\u1eebng lu\u00f4n \u1ea5p \u1ee7 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh \u0111ang gi\u01b0\u01a1ng cao chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i d\u1ef1ng t\u00f3c g\u00e1y, v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1ee1 \u00f2a trong h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. V\u00ec v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ng\u1eebng nu\u00f4i tham v\u1ecdng. Ch\u1eebng n\u00e0o ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 31 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 24/6. V\u00ec th\u1ebf n\u1ebfu c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u1eafm anh c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u1eefa. Tuy nhi\u00ean r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng Argentina s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong n\u0103m nay hay 4 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/tuoi-31-cua-lionel-messi-mot-dam-me-mot-dai-kho-mot-si-389-189418.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/tuoi-31-cua-lionel-messi-mot-dam-me-mot-dai-kho-mot-si.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/tuoi-31-cua-lionel-messi-mot-dam-me-mot-dai-kho-mot-si-389-189418.html\">Tu\u1ed5i 31 c\