u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs Panama b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>\u0110T Anh th\u1eafng 3-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </em>Anh vs Panama<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian:</em> 19h ng\u00e0y 24/6<br>\r\n<em> \u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>S\u00e2n Nizhny Novgorod<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em> TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Anh -0.91*0:1 3/4*0.86 Panama<br>\r\n<em> TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> Nhi\u1ec1u 0.86*2 1/2*-0.93 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o tr\u00ean Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o tr\u00ean Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-panama-va-du-doan-soi-keo-panama-vs-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama 19h ng\u00e0y 24/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1i c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 B\u1ec9 v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Tunisia 5-2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi \u0110T Anh. \u0110\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u00f4 h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Tam s\u01b0 l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00eam n\u1eefa, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Anh \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. \u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Tunisia 2-1 \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 khi l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi 5-2 Tunisia\" title=\"B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/231459-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tunisia 5-2</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb World Cup 2006, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Paraguay 1-0 t\u1edbi nay, \u0110T Anh m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. 2 k\u1ef3 c\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1eeba qua, Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 v\u00e0 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n s\u1edbm. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, v\u1edbi b\u1ec7 ph\u00f3ng l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m khi m\u1edbi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n c\u1ecf n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c l\u1ea1c quan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i suy \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Panama qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi Anh v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n then ch\u1ed1t l\u00e0 b\u1edfi tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb khu v\u1ef1c CONCACAF \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tunisia 1-2 Anh Harry Kane\" title=\"Tunisia 1-2 Anh Harry Kane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/diem-nhan-tran-tunisia-12-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T&nbsp;Anh kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u1edf World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng, Panama v\u1eabn th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u00f4i l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung M\u1ef9 l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu trong c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Panama \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Qua \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Panama b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 v\u00e9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Hernan Gomez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi 3-0 Panama\" title=\"B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Bi-3-0-Panama-Khi-moi-loi-khen-di-kem-voi-mot-chu-nhung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Panama th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-3 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1ecb xem l\u00e0 &ldquo;l\u00f3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng&rdquo; nh\u01b0 Panama l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Anh ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh. V\u1edbi ri\u00eang ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane, anh c\u00f2n m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ri\u00eang l\u00e0 chinh ph\u1ee5c danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi. Kane v\u00e0 Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn khi r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia, Kane \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Romelu Lukaku ghi 4 b\u00e0n sau 2 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ch\u00e2n s\u00fat thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Tottenham \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01a1n th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Kane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf CLB v\u00e0 gi\u1edd ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh r\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y. HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 trao chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Kane v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00e0u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Harry Kane\" title=\"tien dao Harry Kane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/hlv-southgate-phat-bieu-ve-kane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama tin r\u1eb1ng Kane s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i. C\u1ea3 v\u00ec m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea3 v\u00ec \u0110TQG, anh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ghi th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n. C\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 Euro 2016 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean n\u1ed7i \u0111au.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n s\u1edbm ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t &ldquo;\u0111\u00eam d\u00e0i l\u1eafm m\u1ed9ng&rdquo; b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama. M\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra: Sau khi s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Anh \u0111\u1ea9y Panama v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Khi \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea5y tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi Tunisia h\u00f4m qua l\u00e0m v\u00ed d\u1ee5. Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf, nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 thi nhau b\u1eafn ph\u00e1 khung th\u00e0nh Tunisia. Nh\u1eefng m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nh\u01b0 Eden Hazard hay Lukaku \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1edbi m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn Michy Batshuayi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p 2 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 1. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi g\u1ee3i l\u00ean nh\u1eefng suy ngh\u0129 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>\u0110T Anh th\u1eafng 3-0</strong></div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 10 (O 9 1/2)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 5 (O 4 1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Panama trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn s\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n (-1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Panama trong hi\u1ec7p 1 s\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n (-1/4)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Panama trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng thua qu\u00e1 5 (+5)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"534","checkdouble":"189416"},{"date":"13:08 24/06","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-duc-21-thuy-dien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Toni Kroos</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Toni Kroos \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m v\u1edbi Sebastian Rudy, sau khi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Bayern d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm th\u00ec Kroos \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Gundogan. D\u00f9 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o th\u00ec ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real v\u1eabn ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-Duc-vs-Thuy-Dien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Toni Kroos ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7 Toni Kroos th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i v\u1eadt \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, anh v\u1eeba l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng, ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKroos ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 144 l\u1ea7n (nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n), th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 121 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 93.6%. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 17 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111i \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f2n n\u1eefa, Kroos c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng, 3 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 6 qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t. Ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Kroos th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp m\u1eabu m\u1ef1c gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nToni Kroos \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Mesut Ozil hay Thomas Muller m\u00e0 ch\u00ednh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Die Mannschaft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Jerome Boateng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, trong hi\u1ec7p 1 anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n t\u1ecf ra thua thi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111ua t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tinh huong Boateng pham loi voi Forsberg trong vong cam DT Duc\" title=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Boateng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Forsberg trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/130053-boateng.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Boateng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bayern Munich th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Emil Forsberg trong hi\u1ec7p 1, d\u00f9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh song tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng 11m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111ang l\u00e0 1-1 v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u00ec Jerome Boateng l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 2 qua \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea5t may cho Boateng l\u00e0 Toni Kroos \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0110\u1ee9c, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Marco Reus</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1, HLV Joachim Low \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Marco Reus \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u00e1 ngay sau trung phong Timo Werner. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Reus \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup, v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Reus va man tro lai tuyet voi\" title=\"Reus v\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-o-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Reus g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMarco Reus thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, anh t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh. Reus th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Reus. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng sau c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n, sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Dortmund ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap Toni Kroos ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-o-world-cup-421-189402.html\" target=\"_blank\">Reus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span>. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Janne Andersson \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi m\u00e0 c\u00f2n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0 sau 45 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Toivonen mo ty so cho Thuy Dien\" title=\"Toivonen m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/Ola-Toivonen-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Duc-vs-Thuy-Dien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Marco Reus gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1. Tuy nhi\u00ean Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1eabn b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh tri\u1ec3n khai l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00ec \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Toni Kroos \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 cho \u0110\u1ee9c. C\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Janne Andersson trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed5 s\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-duc-vs-thuy-dien-421-189372.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n </span>khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico m\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1eafng tay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Han Quoc vs Mexico\" title=\"H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/223052-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Son Heung-Min kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico. Tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 kim chi \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra. \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n thua Mexico, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Mesut Ozil</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Mexico \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, song m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Low noi ve Mesut Ozil\" title=\"HLV Low n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/hlv-joachim-low-noi-gi-ve-quyet-dinh-loai-bo-mesut-ozil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Mesut Ozil kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ozil ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 1 l\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi\u1ebfn Ozil b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, anh ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Marco Reus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed khi r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng HLV Joachim Low c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hlv-joachim-low-noi-gi-ve-quyet-dinh-loai-bo-mesut-ozil-421-189410.html\" target=\"_blank\">Joachim Low ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ozil</span>, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988, song v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Reus, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng&nbsp;Ozil ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"533","checkdouble":"189417"},{"date":"16:31 24/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Panama e ng\u1ea1i Harry Kane","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/nguoi-cu-panama-e-ngai-harry-kane.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u HLV Julio Dely Valdes c\u1ee7a Panama cho r\u1eb1ng Harry Kane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Kane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Tunisia. Pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd c\u1ee7a Kane \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f9ng kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho Tam S\u01b0 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKane \u0111ang d\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi hi\u1ec7n nay. Anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 20 b\u00e0n trong 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Panama e ng\u1ea1i Kane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Panama e ng\u1ea1i Kane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/nguoi-cu-panama-e-ngai-harry-kane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>C\u1ef1u HLV\u00a0Panama e ng\u1ea1i Kane</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1edbi Panama, Kane s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 l\u0129nh x\u01b0\u1edbng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec3n Anh. V\u00e0 c\u1ef1u HLV Dely Valdes t\u1ecf ra lo ng\u1ea1i cho Panama v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a Kane.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTrong v\u00e0i n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Kane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Anh \u1ea5y ghi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cVai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Kane c\u0169ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n Anh. V\u00e0 Panama ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Kane \u0111\u00e1 r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edf h\u1eefu n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t l\u1eabn k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>2 ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Panama</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Panama \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 Honduras \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1edbi Nga t\u1eeb khu v\u1ef1c CONCACAF. V\u00e0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Panama v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh gi\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Nga. V\u00e0 Dely Valdes \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean then ch\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u M\u0129.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Panama hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1ecf h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jaime Penedo. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cRoman Torres c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 huy c\u1ee7a Panama \u1edf World Cup n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p h\u1ecd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n th\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Anh vs Panama:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-panama-va-du-doan-soi-keo-panama-vs-anh-421-189416.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1edbm Anh vs Panama</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-panama-19h00-ngay-2406-ve-di-tiep-cho-tam-su-421-189401.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama (19h00 ng\u00e0y 24/06): V\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cho Tam s\u01b0?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"532","checkdouble":"189420"},{"date":"16:40 24/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Anh vs Panama 19h00 ng\u00e0y 24/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/link-xem-anh-vs-panama.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Anh vs Panama: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs Panama b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 24/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Anh vs Panama: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs Panama b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 24/6.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-anh-vs-panama-463-189421.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ANH VS PANAMA</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"531","checkdouble":"189421"},{"date":"17:11 24/06","title":"N\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111ang \"r\u1ed1i nh\u01b0 canh h\u1eb9\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/24/noi-bo-tuyen-argentina-dang-roi-nhu-canh-he.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111ang r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng r\u1ed1i ren khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng khai th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t h\u00f2a v\u1edbi HLV Jorge Sampaoli trong khi c\u00e1c quan ch\u1ee9c c\u1ea5p cao l\u1ea1i ch\u01b0a d\u00e1m \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ea1nh tay.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Lionel Messi c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi x\u01b0\u1edbng phi v\u1ee5 \"\u0111\u1ea3o ch\u00ednh\" thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng 58 tu\u1ed5i b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi v\u00e0 b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng 0-3 c\u1ee7a Albiceleste tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, song Argentina v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u1edd v\u1ecb c\u1ee9u tinh mang t\u00ean Nigeria khi \"\u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\" \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111ang r\u1ed1i nh\u01b0 canh h\u1eb9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111ang r\u1ed1i nh\u01b0 canh h\u1eb9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/NINTCHDBPICT0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mascherano \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ea7u vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea3o ch\u00ednh Sampaoli. \u1ea2nh: AFP.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Sampaoli c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Nigeria \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi tr\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee3i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i Iceland vs Croatia \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00ea gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y v\u1eeba qua, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Argentina \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1edbi Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd m\u1ea5t h\u1ebft ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m d\u00e0nh cho \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Sampaoli.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 6 v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a 23 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n, HLV Sampaoli, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina Claudio Tapia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJavier Mascherano \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ea7u phi v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea3o ch\u00ednh, y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nigeria di\u1ec5n ra. H\u1ecd mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorge Barruchaga, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1986, hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG s\u1ebd l\u00ean thay th\u1ebf HLV Sampaoli.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, sau cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i ri\u00eang v\u1edbi Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Tapia, HLV Sampaoli v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Tapia mu\u1ed1n Sampaoli t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0110TQG, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u00ean, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 58 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV Argentina trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a World Cup v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/tuoi-31-cua-lionel-messi-mot-dam-me-mot-dai-kho-mot-si-389-189418.html\">Tu\u1ed5i 31 c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi: M\u1ed9t \u0111am m\u00ea, m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1i kh\u1edd, m\u1ed9t Si</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/fernando-hierro-phat-bieu-ve-dt-argentina-va-messi-421-189405.html\">T\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Argentina y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m, \u0111\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nigeria-20-iceland-dai-bang-cuu-song-argentina-va-messi-421-189323.html\">Nigeria 2-0 Iceland: \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d c\u1ee9u s\u1ed1ng Argentina v\u00e0 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tan-man/argentina-de-thua-croatia-khi-argentina-khong-phu-thuoc-vao-messi-392-189264.html\">Argentina \u0111\u1ec3 thua Croatia: Khi Argentina kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-that-bai-khi-sampaoli-lac-me-hon-tran-421-189252.html\">Argentina th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Khi Sampaoli l\u1ea1c m\u00ea h\u1ed3n tr\u1eadn</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"530","checkdouble":"189422"}]}